				Management and UX Design. Leveraging comprehensive understanding of the product
				development lifecycle to create user-centered web solutions. Strong
				problem-solving abilities with a passion for clean efficient code and intuitive
				user experiences.
			</p>
			<div class="contact">
				<div class="wide">
					<strong>Email</strong>
					<span>callumkloos@gmail.com</span>
				</div>
				<div class="wide">
					<strong>Bluesky</strong>
